==English==

===Noun===
'''homework''' ([[uncountable]])
{{wikipedia}}
#[[Work]] that is done at [[home]], especially [[school]] [[exercise]]s set by a [[teacher]].
#* You must do your '''homework''' before watching the telly.
#[[Preliminary]] or [[preparatory]] work.
#* The speaker had certainly done his '''homework''' before delivering the lecture.

